is the only place he can go.

1:08:40.669 --> 1:08:43.805
Help me, please.
He's in my head, Father.

1:08:43.905 --> 1:08:47.476
Lestat has entered his mind,
heart and soul,

1:08:47.576 --> 1:08:50.178
