feeling great regret.

1:08:50.279 --> 1:08:52.648
I laid down
with the devil.

1:08:52.748 --> 1:08:54.383
Help me!

1:08:54.483 --> 1:08:58.654
I am weak,
and I want to die.

1:08:58.754 --> 1:09:00.922
